# E-Commerce Sales Analytics & Customer Intelligence 

## Overview
Analyzed 541K+ transaction records using 15 advanced SQL queries

## Key Metrics
- Total Revenue: $10.67M
- Total Customers: 4,373
- Total Orders: 22K
- Repeat Customer Rate: 99.50%

## What's Included
- 15 SQL queries covering RFM analysis, CLV, churn detection, revenue trends
- Top 20 customers by spending
- Top 15 products by revenue
- Customer segmentation (VIP/Gold/Regular/At-Risk)
- Monthly trends and seasonal patterns

## Key Insights
✓ Top 26% of customers generate 80% of revenue
✓ 99.50% of customers make repeat purchases
✓ Orders distributed across Low/Medium/High price segments
